\";s:8:\"position\";i:0;s:8:\"settings\";O:8:\"stdClass\":22:{s:4:\"text\";s:2938:\"<h1 id=\"header_container\"><strong>Make a Donation</strong></h1>\nPlease click on this Donate button:\n\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><input name=\"cmd\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"_s-xclick\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><input name=\"hosted_button_id\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"4WRJT6HPADCU8\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><input alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/paypal.jpg\" type=\"image\" /></p>\n\n</form><form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-402\" src=\"http://limmudboston.48in48sites.org/uploads/2017/05/paypal.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"169\" />\n\n</form><form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\">Your LimmudBoston donation helps us continue the work which inspires and unites New England’s many Jewish communities, and helps us continue the core practice of Limmud International, that all who wish to learn can be included, regardless of financial circumstances.\n\nLimmudBoston, Inc. is a 501(c)3 tax exempt organization. Contributions are tax deductible to the extent allowed by law as long as LimmudBoston, Inc. provided no goods or services in exchange for your contribution.\n\nDonations received before November 15 will be acknowledged in the annual LimmudBoston conference program book given to every conference attendee.\n\nPlease consider the following amounts, or choose an amount that fits your wallet:\n\n<strong>Pillars of Learning</strong>, $500 or more, helps to fund a presenter; receives 4 admissions;\n\n<strong>Prophets</strong>, $360-499, receive conference admission for four;\n\n<strong>Scholars</strong>, $180-359, receive conference admission for two;\n\n<strong>Learners</strong>, $118-179, receive conference admission for one;\n\n<strong>Well-Wishers</strong>, $72 &amp; above, will be listed in the LimmudBoston Program Book.\n\n</form><form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"></form><form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\">If you prefer, you can send a check by mail. Please make your check payable to LimmudBoston with “LimmudBoston” in the memo line, and send it to:\n\nLimmudBoston\nPO Box 36\nWaban MA 02468\n\nNotes\n<ol>\n 	<li>Your contribution will be noted in the LimmudBoston Program Book.</li>\n 	<li>Please indicate if you wish to remain anonymous.</li>\n 	<li>If you wish to make a donation in honor of, or in memory of, one or more people, please indicate this and the information will be included.</li>\n 	<li>Sponsorship opportunities are available. For details contact LimmudBoston  <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org </a></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"four columns\"></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n</form>\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"visibility_display\";s:0:\"\";s:26:\"visibility_user_capability\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"animation\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"animation_delay\";s:3:\"0.0\";s:2:\"id\";s:6:\"header\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"rich-text\";s:11:\"connections\";a:1:{s:4:\"text\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:13:\"593343fdeae61\";O:8:\"stdClass\":5:{s:4:\"node\";s:13:\"593343fdeae61\";s:4:\"type\";s:12:\"column-group