a difficult abstract topic - done well.</em></p><p><em>Well organized, lots of info, passionate speakers. Great links between audio / video - the press conference etc... Clearly a labor of love by the presenter.</em></p><p> </p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"> </p>\";}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:11:\"testimonial\";s:403:\"<p><em>Great mix of text study and Philosophy and great ending with an article. Great at including participants. Great job!</em></p><p>Really interesting, presented in an easy to follow and understandable manner, accessible to all levels of Jewish knowledge!</p><p><em>Personal, small, educations, fun, very thought provoking.  Very knowledgeable presenter!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"> </p>\";}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":2:{s:1:\"0\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"testimonial\";s:722:\"<p>Very informative and engaging. I learned new ways of looking at known text.</p><p><em>Made me think differently about the topic and what it means in life.  Also \'bag of connotations\" more broadly - great! Even with my rudimentary Hebrew, I could follow.</em></p><p>Drew attendees into intense discussion, both philosophical and personal. Also helped me re-intererpret familiar passages from the tradition in new ways. Jeremy was very open to discussion and good at leading it.</p><p><em><style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></style>Excellent presentation. Having us write evoked many memories. I learned a lot and have much more information about poetry.</em></p>\";}}s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0