r Friends of LimmudBoston:</h2>\n<div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>LimmudBoston links to your website.</li>\n 	<li>Your organization is mentioned in LimmudBoston program book and literature.</li>\n 	<li>You are recognized as part of the LimmudBoston community.</li>\n 	<li>Tickets to the annual conference</li>\n 	<li>Mentions online and in the Program Book</li>\n 	<li>Recognition as part of the LimmudBoston community</li>\n 	<li>Invitations to Advisory Team and other events</li>\n</ul>\nIf you have questions about becoming a Friend of LimmudBoston, write to <a href=\"mailto:info@limmudboston.org\">info@limmudboston.org</a>\n\n</div>\nOrganizational support helps LimmudBoston continue to provide educational programs that stimulate and engage learners of all ages. We are pleased to provide the following benefits to our Friends for their generous contributions.\n<h3 class=\"friend2\">Pillars $500 and above</h3>\nAn organizational contribution at this level includes four (4) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend3\">Prophets $360 and above</h3>\nAn organizational contribution at this level includes four (4) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend4\">Scholars $180 – $359</h3>\nAn organizational contribution at this level provides two (2) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend5\">Learners $118 – $179</h3>\nAn organizational contribution at this level provides a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend6\">Well-wishers $72 – $117</h3>\n<h2 class=\"friends-final\">Friends of LimmudBoston have just a few responsibilities:</h2>\n<div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Link to the LimmudBoston website — in exchange for our linking to your website.</li>\n 	<li>Designate a key contact for LimmudBoston communication.</li>\n 	<li>Recruit volunticipants from your organization to join LimmudBoston committees (at least one, possibly more).</li>\n 	<li>Promote LimmudBoston in your newsletters and communications.</li>\n 	<li>Support LimmudBoston financially.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n\nFeel free to email <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> with any questions.\n\nPlease add the banner at the top of this page to your website. You can download it by clicking <a title=\"\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Friends_logo.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-0\" data-imagelightbox=\"0\">here.</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"four columns\">\n<div id=\"sidebar\">\n<div id=\"text-5\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\n\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"visibility_display\";s:0:\"\";s:26:\"visibility_user_capability\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"animation\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"animation_delay\";s:3:\"0.0\";s:2:\"id\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"rich-text\";s:11:\"connections\";a:1:{s:4:\