lus a Program Book listing and an active link in large font to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend4\">Scholars $180 – $359</h3>\nAn organizational contribution at this level provides two (2) tickets to the LimmudBoston conference, lunch, plus a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend5\">Learners $118 – $179</h3>\nAn organizational contribution at this level provides a Program Book listing and an active link to your organization on the LimmudBoston website in the Friends section.\n<h3 class=\"friend6\">Well-wishers $72 – $117</h3>\n<h2 class=\"friends-final\">Friends of LimmudBoston have just a few responsibilities:</h2>\n<div>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Link to the LimmudBoston website — in exchange for our linking to your website.</li>\n 	<li>Designate a key contact for LimmudBoston communication.</li>\n 	<li>Recruit volunticipants from your organization to join LimmudBoston committees (at least one, possibly more).</li>\n 	<li>Promote LimmudBoston in your newsletters and communications.</li>\n 	<li>Support LimmudBoston financially.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n\nFeel free to email <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org</a> with any questions.\n\nPlease add the banner at the top of this page to your website. You can download it by clicking <a title=\"\" href=\"https://limmudboston.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Friends_logo.jpg\" data-rel=\"lightbox-0\" data-imagelightbox=\"0\">here.</a>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"four columns\">\n<div id=\"sidebar\">\n<div id=\"text-5\" class=\"widget-container-primary widget_text\">\n<h3 class=\"widget-title\">Thank You Friends and Supporters!</h3>\n<div class=\"textwidget\">\n\n<a href=\"https://limmudboston.org/support/become-a-friend/support/supporters\">Friends and Supporters from previous years</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margi