;\n\n<strong>Prophets</strong>, $360-499, receive conference admission for four;\n\n<strong>Scholars</strong>, $180-359, receive conference admission for two;\n\n<strong>Learners</strong>, $118-179, receive conference admission for one;\n\n<strong>Well-Wishers</strong>, $72 &amp; above, will be listed in the LimmudBoston Program Book.\n\n</form><form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\"></form><form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\">If you prefer, you can send a check by mail. Please make your check payable to LimmudBoston with “LimmudBoston” in the memo line, and send it to:\n\nLimmudBoston\nPO Box 36\nWaban MA 02468\n\nNotes\n<ol>\n 	<li>Your contribution will be noted in the LimmudBoston Program Book.</li>\n 	<li>Please indicate if you wish to remain anonymous.</li>\n 	<li>If you wish to make a donation in honor of, or in memory of, one or more people, please indicate this and the information will be included.</li>\n 	<li>Sponsorship opportunities are available. For details contact LimmudBoston  <a href=\"mailto:info@LimmudBoston.org\">info@LimmudBoston.org </a></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n<div class=\"four columns\"></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n</form>\";s:10:\"margin_top\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"margin_top_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"margin_top_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"margin_bottom\";s:0:\"\";s:20:\"margin_bottom_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:24:\"margin_bottom_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"margin_left\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"margin_left_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"margin_left_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"margin_right\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"margin_right_medium\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"margin_right_responsive\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"responsive_display\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"visibility_display\";s:0:\"\";s:26:\"visibility_user_capability\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"animation\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"animation_delay\";s:3:\"0.0\";s:2:\"id\";s:6:\"header\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"rich-text\";s:11:\"connections\";a:1:{s: